'''佛羅勒斯人'''（[[学名|学名]]：''{{lang|la|Homo floresiensis}}''）是近年发现的一种史前人类，为[[人属|人属]]的一种，主要特征是体型小，[[大脑|大脑]]小，因此也被化名作「[[哈比人|哈比人]]」。<ref name="Brown04">{{Cite journal|title=A new small-bodied hominin from the Late Pleistocene of Flores, Indonesia|url=http://www.nature.com/articles/nature02999|last=Brown|first=P.|last2=Sutikna|first2=T.|date=2004-10|journal=Nature|issue=7012|doi=10.1038/nature02999|volume=431|pages=1055–1061|language=en|issn=0028-0836|last3=Morwood|first3=M. J.|last4=Soejono|first4=R. P.|last5=Jatmiko|last6=Wayhu Saptomo|first6=E.|last7=Awe Due|first7=Rokus|access-date=2021-08-30|archive-date=2022-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220515184953/https://www.nature.com/articles/nature02999}}</ref><ref name="Morwood04">{{Cite journal|title=Archaeology and age of a new hominin from Flores in eastern Indonesia|url=http://www.nature.com/articles/nature02956|last=Morwood|first=M. J.|last2=Soejono|first2=R. P.|date=2004-10|journal=Nature|issue=7012|doi=10.1038/nature02956|volume=431|pages=1087–1091|language=en|issn=0028-0836|last3=Roberts|first3=R. G.|last4=Sutikna|first4=T.|last5=Turney|first5=C. S. M.|last6=Westaway|first6=K. E.|last7=Rink|first7=W. J.|last8=Zhao|first8=J.- x.|last9=van den Bergh|first9=G. D.|access-date=2021-08-30|archive-date=2022-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220514034840/https://www.nature.com/articles/nature02956}}</ref>他们居住在[[印度尼西亚|印尼]][[弗洛勒斯島|弗洛勒斯島]]上，原本認為可能约12000年前[[滅絕|滅絕]]，因此可能与现代[[人类|人类]]共存一段很久的時間，是已绝种[[人屬|人屬]]中存活時間最晚的。但最新的研究指出佛羅勒斯人可能在現代人類5萬年前到達該地區時不久就[[滅絕|滅絕]]了。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Indonesian 'Hobbits' may have died out sooner than thought|url=https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2016/03/160330135304.htm|access-date=2021-08-30|work=ScienceDaily|language=en|archive-date=2019-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190712162718/https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2016/03/160330135304.htm}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=霍比特人生活在距今70万年前|url=http://www.solidot.org/story?sid=48539|accessdate=2016-07-08|publisher=Solidot|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170109072058/http://www.solidot.org/story?sid=48539|archive-date=2017-01-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>

佛羅勒斯人在基因上与[[丹尼索瓦人|丹尼索瓦人]]和[[尼安德特人|尼安德特人]]有混合的历史<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Evolutionary history and adaptation of a human pygmy population of Flores Island, Indonesia|url=https://www.sciencemag.org/lookup/doi/10.1126/science.aar8486|last=Tucci|first=Serena|last2=Vohr|first2=Samuel H.|date=2018-08-03|journal=Science|issue=6401|doi=10.1126/science.aar8486|volume=361|pages=511–516|language=en|issn=0036-8075|pmc=PMC6709593|pmid=30072539|last3=McCoy|first3=Rajiv C.|last4=Vernot|first4=Benjamin|last5=Robinson|first5=Matthew R.|last6=Barbieri|first6=Chiara|last7=Nelson|first7=Brad J.|last8=Fu|first8=Wenqing|last9=Purnomo|first9=Gludhug A.}}</ref>。

